# Fullstack Web Developer Roadmap ðŸš€

This roadmap is designed to guide you from foundational knowledge to mastering the skills of a fullstack web developer. Follow this structured path to gain the necessary expertise in both frontend and backend development.

---

## ðŸŽ¨ Color Coding Explanation

- **(Recommended)** These are highly recommended skills or technologies based on industry standards and trends.
- **(Alternative)** These are optional alternatives; you can choose them based on your preferences or project needs.
- **(Anytime Learning)** These skills can be learned in any order depending on your progress and requirements.

---

